WEBVTT

00:00:29.797 --> 00:00:31.998
na mahitaji ya maisha kwa mwingine.

00:00:32.618 --> 00:00:35.163
Sawa, ntafanya nini ?

00:00:35.187 --> 00:00:37.116
Nitanunua dawa

00:00:37.140 --> 00:00:38.774
ama kulipa bili zangu?

00:00:39.340 --> 00:00:41.952
Na siwezi ishi bila dawa zangu,

00:00:41.976 --> 00:00:44.666
na sitaishi bila kulipa bili zangu."

00:00:45.065 --> 00:00:49.469
Watu elfu kumi wanafariki 
kila mwezi hapa nchini,

00:00:49.493 --> 00:00:52.068
kwa sababu hawatumii
dawa inavyostahili,

00:00:52.623 --> 00:00:55.929
Watu wengi hufa
kwa kutomeza dawa

00:00:55.953 --> 00:01:00.707
kuzidi utumizi wa afyuni kupita kiwango
na ajali za barabara zikijumuishwa